/**
 * Gamification constants: XP, levels, achievements, power-ups, and challenges
 */

import { Achievement, DailyChallenge, PowerUp } from '../types';

// XP Configuration
export const XP_PER_LEVEL_BASE = 200;
export const XP_PER_TASK = 15;

// Power-up definitions
export const POWER_UPS: PowerUp[] = [
  {
    id: 'streak_x2',
    name: 'Streak Multiplier x2',
    description: 'Double XP for completed tasks when streak is active',
    icon: 'üî•',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 2,
    duration: 30,
    requiredLevel: 1,
  },
  {
    id: 'bonus_x15',
    name: 'Bonus XP +15',
    description: 'Get +15 XP on every task completion',
    icon: '‚ú®',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 1,
    duration: 60,
    requiredLevel: 3,
  },
  {
    id: 'streak_x3',
    name: 'Legendary Streak x3',
    description: 'Triple XP for ultra-hot streaks (14+ days)',
    icon: '‚ö°',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 3,
    duration: 15,
    requiredLevel: 5,
  },
  {
    id: 'focus_mode',
    name: 'Focus Mode',
    description: '2x XP for high priority tasks',
    icon: 'üéØ',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 2,
    duration: 45,
    requiredLevel: 7,
  },
  // New Power-ups from Phase 3
  {
    id: 'xp_surge',
    name: 'XP Surge',
    description: 'Triple XP for 30 minutes',
    icon: 'üí´',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 3,
    duration: 30,
    requiredLevel: 10,
    rarity: 'epic',
  },
  {
    id: 'streak_shield',
    name: 'Streak Shield',
    description: 'Protect streak for one missed day',
    icon: 'üõ°Ô∏è',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 1,
    duration: 0, // One-time use
    requiredLevel: 15,
    rarity: 'rare',
  },
  {
    id: 'task_magnet',
    name: 'Task Magnet',
    description: 'Auto-complete 3 random low-priority tasks',
    icon: 'üß≤',
    active: false,
    multiplier: 1,
    duration: 0, // Instant use
    requiredLevel: 20,
    rarity: 'legendary',
  },
];

// Achievement definitions
export const INITIAL_ACHIEVEMENTS: Achievement[] = [
  // Original Achievements
  { id: 'first_step', title: 'First Step', description: 'Complete your first task', icon: 'üëã', unlocked: false, points: 50, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'collector', title: 'Task Collector', description: 'Complete 10 tasks total', icon: 'üì¶', unlocked: false, points: 100, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'organizer', title: 'Organizer', description: 'Complete 25 tasks total', icon: 'üìã', unlocked: false, points: 200, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'master_doer', title: 'Master Doer', description: 'Complete 100 tasks total', icon: '‚öîÔ∏è', unlocked: false, points: 500, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'productivity_guru', title: 'Productivity Guru', description: 'Complete 250 tasks total', icon: 'üéì', unlocked: false, points: 1000, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'legendary', title: 'Legendary', description: 'Complete 500 tasks total', icon: 'üåü', unlocked: false, points: 2500, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'streak_start', title: 'Streak Starter', description: 'Maintain a 3-day streak', icon: 'üî•', unlocked: false, points: 100, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'streak_master', title: 'Streak Master', description: 'Maintain a 7-day streak', icon: '‚ö°', unlocked: false, points: 250, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'streak_master_2', title: 'Streak Grandmaster', description: 'Maintain a 14-day streak', icon: 'üíé', unlocked: false, points: 500, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'streak_legend', title: 'Streak Legend', description: 'Maintain a 30-day streak', icon: 'üëë', unlocked: false, points: 1000, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'streak_immortal', title: 'Streak Immortal', description: 'Maintain a 60-day streak', icon: 'üöÄ', unlocked: false, points: 2500, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'early_bird', title: 'Early Bird', description: 'Complete a task before 9 AM', icon: 'üåÖ', unlocked: false, points: 75, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'night_owl', title: 'Night Owl', description: 'Complete a task after 9 PM', icon: 'üåô', unlocked: false, points: 75, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'high_performer', title: 'High Performer', description: 'Complete 5 high priority tasks', icon: 'üéØ', unlocked: false, points: 150, unlockedAt: undefined },
  { id: 'high_master', title: 'High Master', description: 'Complete 20 high priority tasks', icon: 'üî•', unlocked: false, points: 400, unlockedAt: undefined },

  // New Phase 3 Achievements
  { id: 'early_bird_planner', title: 'Early Bird Planner', description: 'Schedule 5 tasks before 7 AM', icon: 'üêì', unlocked: false, points: 150, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'productivity' },
  { id: 'weekend_warrior', title: 'Weekend Warrior', description: 'Complete tasks on Saturday AND Sunday', icon: 'üèÜ', unlocked: false, points: 100, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'productivity' },
  { id: 'perfectionist', title: 'Perfectionist', description: 'Complete all daily challenges for 7 days in a row', icon: 'üíØ', unlocked: false, points: 500, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'dedication' },
  { id: 'speed_demon', title: 'Speed Demon', description: 'Complete 5 tasks in 30 minutes', icon: '‚ö°', unlocked: false, points: 100, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'productivity' },
  { id: 'marathon_runner', title: 'Marathon Runner', description: 'Complete 10+ Pomodoro sessions in one day', icon: 'üèÉ', unlocked: false, points: 200, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'focus' },
  { id: 'calendar_pro', title: 'Calendar Pro', description: 'Use calendar view for 30 consecutive days', icon: 'üìÖ', unlocked: false, points: 300, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'organization' },
  { id: 'zero_inbox', title: 'Zero Inbox', description: 'Complete all tasks for the day', icon: 'üì≠', unlocked: false, points: 75, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'productivity' },
  { id: 'multi_tasker', title: 'Multi-tasker', description: 'Have 10 tasks in progress at once', icon: 'üé≠', unlocked: false, points: 50, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'organization' },
  { id: 'quick_draw', title: 'Quick Draw', description: 'Create and complete a task within 5 minutes', icon: 'ü§†', unlocked: false, points: 25, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'productivity' },
  { id: 'zen_master', title: 'Zen Master', description: 'Maintain a 60-day streak (ultimate dedication)', icon: 'üßò', unlocked: false, points: 1000, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'dedication' },
  { id: 'keyboard_master', title: 'Keyboard Master', description: 'Use 100 keyboard shortcuts', icon: '‚å®Ô∏è', unlocked: false, points: 250, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'efficiency' },
  { id: 'power_user', title: 'Power User', description: 'Use 20 keyboard shortcuts', icon: 'üí™', unlocked: false, points: 75, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'efficiency' },
  { id: 'drag_master', title: 'Drag Master', description: 'Drag 50 tasks to organize', icon: 'üñ±Ô∏è', unlocked: false, points: 50, unlockedAt: undefined, category: 'organization' },
];

// Daily challenge definitions
export const INITIAL_CHALLENGES: DailyChallenge[] = [
  { id: 'daily_1', title: 'Morning Boost', description: 'Complete 2 tasks by 12 PM', target: 2, current: 0, completed: false, reward: 50, icon: '‚òÄÔ∏è' },
  { id: 'daily_2', title: 'Afternoon Push', description: 'Complete 3 tasks by 6 PM', target: 3, current: 0, completed: false, reward: 75, icon: '‚ö°' },
  { id: 'daily_3', title: 'Evening Wind Down', description: 'Complete 1 more task today', target: 1, current: 0, completed: false, reward: 25, icon: 'üåô' },
  { id: 'daily_4', title: 'Focus Hour', description: 'Complete 2 Pomodoro sessions', target: 2, current: 0, completed: false, reward: 100, icon: 'üçÖ' },
];
